\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {DexSafeDAgger overview.} We propose a teacher-intervened online distillation pipeline that condenses teacher skills into a deployable RGB-based student policy. The unsafe exploration rate is substantially suppressed in the early training phase via a customized intervention mechanism that combines teacher--student action disagreement with a learned risk predictor.}}{1}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
